                                        <th>Months</th>
                                        <th>Collection Dates</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr><td>I Quarter</td><td>April–June 2019</td><td>16–24 April 2019</td></tr>
                                    <tr><td>II Quarter</td><td>July–Sept 2019</td><td>09–18 July 2019</td></tr>
                                    <tr><td>III Quarter</td><td>Oct–Dec 2019</td><td>09–18 Oct 2019</td></tr>
                                    <tr><td>IV Quarter</td><td>Jan–Mar 2020</td><td>09–18 Jan 2020</td></tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Payment Info -->
            <div class="tab-pane fade" id="payment-info" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="payment-tab">
                <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 mt-3">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title fw-semibold text-primary">Online Payment Instructions</h5>
                        <p>Dear Parents and Students,</p>
                        <p>AF School Yelahanka has tied up with <strong>HDFC Bank EduQfix</strong> for online school fee payment:</p>
                        <ul class="mb-3">
                            <li>Click the header tab above to go to the HDFC link to make payment.</li>
                            <li>Download the “Qfix” app from the Play Store to remit fees online.</li>
                            <li>Online payment window for II Quarter: <strong>09–18 July 2019</strong>.</li>
                            <li><strong>Late fee of ₹50</strong> will apply from 25 July 2019.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
